### 144.

The eye which looks (at a spot) half way between the shadow and the
light which

<span id="page_85">p. 85</span>

surrounds the body in shadow will see that the deepest shadows on that
body will meet

<span id="img_v108500"></span> ![](img/v108500.jpg)

the eye at equal angles, that is at the same angle as that of sight.

